Derivation and attribution
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This program is a derivative work of the official 17Lands MTG Arena log client:

    mtga-log-client
    https://github.com/rconroy293/mtga-log-client
    Copyright (C) its authors (rconroy293)
    Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0

seventeenlands-rust is a Rust port of that client. It deliberately mirrors the
upstream implementation's behavior — message parsing, dispatch order, payload
construction, and other details — so that it remains wire-compatible with the
17Lands API. Because it reproduces protected expression from the upstream
source, it is a derivative work and is therefore distributed under the same
GNU General Public License v3.0 terms as the original.

